GQ magazine has given United States President Donald Trump the ultimate virtual makeover. 
 
With the headline, , the magazine has shown what an impact a little tailoring and a different haircut can make. 
 
The clip shows what the President would look like with less copper-toned skin, and yes, a brand new hairdo. 
 
But GQ also offers Trump several clothing tips, including opting for slimmer pants to avoid wrinkling. 
 
